[Episode 11]

3
00:01:46,479 --> 00:01:48,680
Is that storyteller at Chunfeng Garden

4
00:01:49,270 --> 00:01:50,670
still performing there?

5
00:01:53,229 --> 00:01:54,160
Yes, he still is.

6
00:01:55,050 --> 00:01:56,509
Full audience every day.

7
00:01:57,840 --> 00:01:59,640
Now the entire Imperial Capital

8
00:01:59,759 --> 00:02:01,960
believes that Lord Si Yilin
and Lord Li Qing

9
00:02:01,960 --> 00:02:03,840
are a match made in heaven.

10
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:07,760
However, as a result,

11
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:09,979
I'm afraid that in the Imperial Capital,

12
00:02:09,979 --> 00:02:12,640
no one would dare to pursue
Lord Li Qing anymore.

13
00:02:14,150 --> 00:02:15,520
Do you think so too?

14
00:02:16,680 --> 00:02:17,430
Yes, indeed.

15
00:02:18,430 --> 00:02:20,800
With Lord Si Yilin as such a fine example,

16
00:02:21,160 --> 00:02:23,350
who would dare to be so tactless as to

17
00:02:23,430 --> 00:02:25,680
try to win Lord Li Qing's favor?

18
00:02:27,240 --> 00:02:30,220
How do you think Qing's situation is now?

19
00:02:32,320 --> 00:02:35,320
The reputation of their union
has spread far and wide.

20
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:38,680
Unless you arrange another
marriage for her, My Lord,

21
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:40,400
to suppress the gossip,

22
00:02:41,870 --> 00:02:44,470
Lord Li Qing

23
00:02:44,470 --> 00:02:47,600
will likely have to bear this
reputation indefinitely.

24
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:49,240
That's good then.

25
00:02:51,120 --> 00:02:52,720
Since You can see it clearly,

26
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:56,470
I believe Si Yilin can see it clearly too.

27
00:02:59,910 --> 00:03:02,960
However, given Lord Si Yilin's
temperament,

28
00:03:03,590 --> 00:03:06,430
he wouldn't let others suffer
on his account.

29
00:03:10,080 --> 00:03:12,280
Among the younger generation of Zichuan,

30
00:03:12,280 --> 00:03:14,630
the most capable ones are

31
00:03:14,630 --> 00:03:17,030
the three brothers,

32
00:03:17,050 --> 00:03:18,910
Di Lin, Si Yilin, and Zichuan Xiu.

33
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:22,190
As for Di Lin, he's deep in thought,

34
00:03:22,910 --> 00:03:25,040
and sometimes, even I can't figure out

35
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:28,240
what's on his mind.

36
00:03:29,520 --> 00:03:30,840
As for Zichuan Xiu...

37
00:03:35,120 --> 00:03:36,520
Let's not talk about him.

38
00:03:37,320 --> 00:03:38,890
He's already a traitor.

39
00:03:41,910 --> 00:03:43,310
As for Si Yilin,

40
00:03:44,800 --> 00:03:46,240
my only hope is that

41
00:03:46,750 --> 00:03:50,010
he can remain consistent throughout.

42
00:03:51,710 --> 00:03:53,630
If he could join hands with Qing,

43
00:03:54,710 --> 00:03:56,770
it would surely stabilize the court.

44
00:04:00,960 --> 00:04:04,410
They're obviously the perfect match,

45
00:04:04,430 --> 00:04:07,360
yet he has to make me worry
about this for him.

46
00:04:08,100 --> 00:04:09,220
It's really...

47
00:04:10,590 --> 00:04:12,520
My Lord, you're doing this
for their own good.

48
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:15,030
I believe they will understand one day.

49
00:04:15,660 --> 00:04:19,860
Yes. I hope so.

50
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:38,630
Previously, Uncle ordered me

51
00:04:38,630 --> 00:04:40,370
to oversee the renovation of
the Wayun Fortress.

52
00:04:40,370 --> 00:04:42,370
Lord Di Lin was once stationed here,

53
00:04:42,430 --> 00:04:44,240
so I came specially today

54
00:04:44,240 --> 00:04:45,630
to seek some advice.

55
00:04:47,310 --> 00:04:49,600
The Wayun Fortress is located in
a strategically crucial position,

56
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:51,390
easy to defend but difficult to attack.

57
00:04:51,390 --> 00:04:52,800
However, after years of warfare

58
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:54,060
and multiple battles,

59
00:04:54,120 --> 00:04:56,830
key locations throughout the city
have all been compromised.

60
00:04:56,830 --> 00:04:59,870
The eastern city wall, in particular,
is the most severely damaged.

61
00:04:59,870 --> 00:05:01,480
Although it was repaired
before the battle,

62
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:02,800
it was only an emergency fix.

63
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:05,930
To fully repair it would require
a large amount of funds.

64
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:10,160
But now that the war has just ended,

65
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:12,040
Wayun's treasury is completely empty.

66
00:05:12,040 --> 00:05:14,700
Our clan can hardly afford
any expenses either.

67
00:05:15,070 --> 00:05:16,120
So this matter

68
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:18,270
is a hot potato to begin with.

69
00:05:21,430 --> 00:05:23,000
If we could squeeze some money

70
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:24,270
from Lord Ge Shan,

71
00:05:24,270 --> 00:05:27,330
Uncle wouldn't have sent me here
to handle this matter.

72
00:05:27,560 --> 00:05:29,830
Previously, Lord Si Yilin and Lord Di Lin,

73
00:05:29,830 --> 00:05:32,600
you worked together to handle
Gu Lan's corruption case.

74
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:34,430
The political atmosphere in the court
has greatly changed.

75
00:05:34,430 --> 00:05:37,030
Now, if we want to target
those high officials,

76
00:05:37,050 --> 00:05:38,320
I'm afraid I can only

77
00:05:38,390 --> 00:05:40,790
issue a few medals for honest officialdom.

78
00:05:41,430 --> 00:05:44,560
It seems I'll have to find a way
to raise the money myself.

79
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:47,200
This is the most tricky part
of this matter.

80
00:05:47,430 --> 00:05:49,070
In the past, Zichuan was prosperous.

81
00:05:49,070 --> 00:05:50,750
Not only in government, but even
more so in commerce.

82
00:05:50,750 --> 00:05:53,150
Before Gu Lan, the clan
had immense wealth.

83
00:05:53,190 --> 00:05:54,800
It wasn't just through heavy taxation
and extortion,

84
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:56,390
but more through collusion
between officials and merchants.

85
00:05:56,390 --> 00:05:57,190
That's right.

86
00:05:57,830 --> 00:06:00,120
Now, only the Three Central Offices

87
00:06:00,310 --> 00:06:01,970
can plug this gap for the clan.

88
00:06:03,560 --> 00:06:04,560
After the war,

89
00:06:04,730 --> 00:06:06,750
our clan's power and the nation's strength
were greatly diminished.

90
00:06:06,750 --> 00:06:08,510
But those nobles in the
Three Central Offices

91
00:06:08,510 --> 00:06:10,720
still frequently build mansions

92
00:06:10,830 --> 00:06:12,490
and expand their residences.

93
00:06:13,040 --> 00:06:14,950
So they should be the ones to pay for it.

94
00:06:14,950 --> 00:06:16,410
I think this is a good idea.

95
00:06:16,920 --> 00:06:18,320
But there's one problem.

96
00:06:18,600 --> 00:06:20,730
Those people only take and never give.

97
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:22,750
Without some forceful measures,

98
00:06:22,750 --> 00:06:25,080
I'm afraid they won't be easy
to deal with.

99
00:06:28,390 --> 00:06:30,560
Princess Ning, do you have any plans?

100
00:06:31,070 --> 00:06:35,920
Send a petition first. Show courtesy
before resorting to arms.

101
00:06:36,070 --> 00:06:38,310
If we want to extract funds from
the Three Central Offices,

102
00:06:38,310 --> 00:06:39,510
it won't be easy, of course.

103
00:06:39,510 --> 00:06:41,190
But we need to make them realize

104
00:06:41,190 --> 00:06:42,159
that their money

105
00:06:42,159 --> 00:06:43,820
isn't all rightfully earned.

106
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:46,560
If they're willing to hand over the money
obediently, that's fine.

107
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:48,050
If they're not willing,

108
00:06:48,120 --> 00:06:50,480
in the past, when Zichuan
faced great disasters,

109
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:52,950
the clan temporarily nationalized
the salt and mining industries

110
00:06:52,950 --> 00:06:55,010
to replenish the national treasury.

111
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:57,380
Father did this when he was still around.

112
00:06:57,800 --> 00:06:59,720
If they don't want to cut off
their own profits

113
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:01,390
by sticking to old practices,

114
00:07:01,830 --> 00:07:04,160
then they'd better show some sincerity.

115
00:07:10,510 --> 00:07:11,310
Si Yilin.

116
00:07:12,310 --> 00:07:14,750
Your complexion looks good today.

117
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:18,390
The way you looked so depressed
a few days ago,

118
00:07:18,680 --> 00:07:20,410
I was really worried about you.

119
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:21,820
Who would have thought

120
00:07:21,930 --> 00:07:24,360
the Tiger of Zichuan had this side to him?

121
00:07:26,430 --> 00:07:28,240
Sorry for making you worry,
Lord Chieftain.

122
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:29,310
I'm alright now.

123
00:07:31,070 --> 00:07:33,750
When you live to my age,
you'll understand.

124
00:07:34,870 --> 00:07:37,130
There's no love that can't be forgotten,

125
00:07:37,190 --> 00:07:38,990
and no person who can't be let go.

126
00:07:39,070 --> 00:07:43,040
It's all just a struggle with
one's own obsessions.

127
00:07:44,310 --> 00:07:47,720
By the way, the battle report on
the conflict with the Liufeng family...

128
00:07:47,720 --> 00:07:49,520
It was my oversight.
I'll get it done right away.

129
00:07:49,520 --> 00:07:50,480
No, no.

130
00:07:51,480 --> 00:07:53,540
I only mentioned this to tell you that

131
00:07:53,560 --> 00:07:56,240
Qing has already written it for you.

132
00:07:56,360 --> 00:08:00,420
You only need to go to the Ministry of
Government Supervision and sign it.

133
00:08:00,510 --> 00:08:01,960
This girl Qing,

134
00:08:02,750 --> 00:08:03,950
she's just like that.

135
00:08:04,390 --> 00:08:06,310
Always doing things quietly,

136
00:08:07,110 --> 00:08:09,040
and never mentioning it.

137
00:08:09,310 --> 00:08:10,270
This kid,

138
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:11,770
I really admire her.

139
00:08:12,480 --> 00:08:15,210
After you recaptured the
three cities this time,

140
00:08:15,790 --> 00:08:18,520
everyone in the court and beyond
was full of praise,

141
00:08:18,520 --> 00:08:20,740
and your marriage was brought up again.

142
00:08:22,070 --> 00:08:24,000
But Qing told me

143
00:08:24,340 --> 00:08:25,650
not to mention it anymore.

144
00:08:25,650 --> 00:08:27,090
I asked her why.

145
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:30,820
She said she didn't want to put you
in a difficult position.

146
00:08:33,539 --> 00:08:34,940
But who would comfort her

147
00:08:35,250 --> 00:08:38,120
for the grievances she's endured?

148
00:08:41,270 --> 00:08:43,870
Alright. You young people

149
00:08:44,500 --> 00:08:46,500
handle your own affairs.

150
00:08:47,080 --> 00:08:49,670
I'm just here nagging a little.

151
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:55,270
Someone actually released a Sky Lantern
in the Imperial Capital.

152
00:09:55,270 --> 00:09:56,270
What's going on?

153
00:09:57,550 --> 00:09:58,390
Lord Si Yilin.

154
00:09:58,550 --> 00:09:59,350
Bring it here.

155
00:10:01,440 --> 00:10:02,080
My Lord.

156
00:10:02,850 --> 00:10:04,650
We don't know when this got here.

157
00:10:11,270 --> 00:10:12,800
It probably drifted in from
outside the city.

158
00:10:12,800 --> 00:10:15,170
Go on, don't delay your duties.

159
00:10:15,370 --> 00:10:15,900
Yes.

160
00:10:31,870 --> 00:10:32,730
Your Highness.

161
00:10:33,670 --> 00:10:36,030
It was my fault for accidentally releasing
the Sky Lantern.

162
00:10:36,030 --> 00:10:41,030
I will go to the Ministry of Military and Legal Affairs
tomorrow to receive my punishment.

