♪ It's you ♪

178
00:11:35,400 --> 00:11:37,030
I'll have to face in this world.

179
00:11:37,030 --> 00:11:40,720
♪ In my world,
you're like cloud and mist ♪

180
00:11:40,750 --> 00:11:44,350
♪ Coming and going, so distant ♪

181
