♪ Let love bear witness ♪

189
00:13:00,390 --> 00:13:01,910
You've visited all the nobles of
the Three Central Offices

190
00:13:01,910 --> 00:13:03,310
in the Imperial Capital?

191
00:13:03,440 --> 00:13:05,100
And you've only got this much?

192
00:13:08,630 --> 00:13:11,360
Chief Advisor Xiao claimed to be ill
and refused to see anyone.

193
00:13:11,360 --> 00:13:13,090
Most of the other advisors said

194
00:13:13,750 --> 00:13:16,080
that this is all they have left
in savings.

195
00:13:16,440 --> 00:13:18,870
Advisor He even kicked us out

196
00:13:19,480 --> 00:13:21,350
and injured the attendant
who went with us.

197
00:13:21,350 --> 00:13:22,210
He also said...

198
00:13:23,480 --> 00:13:25,610
That Your Highness hasn't even
ascended to the throne yet,

199
00:13:25,610 --> 00:13:27,320
but is already asserting your authority
and exploiting people,

200
00:13:27,320 --> 00:13:29,680
which is disrespectful and defiant
to the martyrs of Zichuan.

201
00:13:29,680 --> 00:13:32,540
Absurd! How dare he slander
Her Highness like that!

202
00:13:32,840 --> 00:13:37,770
He should be sent directly to the Ministry of
Military and Legal Affairs for punishment.

203
00:13:42,560 --> 00:13:43,670
Advisor He knows

204
00:13:43,840 --> 00:13:47,370
that the reason why Lord Chieftain
sent me to handle this matter

205
00:13:47,600 --> 00:13:49,860
is that he cannot personally intervene.

206
00:13:49,870 --> 00:13:51,800
Issuing a decree to collect money,

207
00:13:54,440 --> 00:13:55,960
I have no legal support,

208
00:13:56,320 --> 00:13:58,080
nor do I have any power to rely on.

209
00:13:58,080 --> 00:14:00,720
Of course he dares to speak brazenly
and without fear.

210
00:14:00,720 --> 00:14:02,920
It's because my foundation is too weak.

211
00:14:03,270 --> 00:14:04,930
I simply can't hold them down.

212
00:14:09,720 --> 00:14:11,550
Have you visited Mr. Ma, Ma Wei?

213
00:14:12,120 --> 00:14:12,980
What did he say?

214
00:14:13,030 --> 00:14:15,390
I have. The housekeeper of the
Ma Residence said

215
00:14:15,390 --> 00:14:17,630
that Mr. Ma Wei is out on a business trip

216
00:14:17,630 --> 00:14:19,760
and won't be back until the afternoon.

217
00:14:25,390 --> 00:14:26,510
Prepare the carriage.

218
00:14:26,510 --> 00:14:27,840
I'll make a visit to the Ma Residence
myself.

219
00:14:27,840 --> 00:14:28,570
Yes, My Lady.

220
00:14:30,720 --> 00:14:33,010
If Your Highness has something
you want to say,

221
00:14:33,010 --> 00:14:34,270
I can convey it for you.

222
00:14:43,240 --> 00:14:43,920
I know

223
00:14:44,730 --> 00:14:47,390
you're worried that others
will speak ill of me.

224
00:14:52,040 --> 00:14:53,670
But if I go in person,

225
00:14:54,290 --> 00:14:56,490
Ma Wei will have to show me some respect.

226
00:14:57,430 --> 00:15:00,560
Most of the Three Central Offices still
paid some money.

227
00:15:00,870 --> 00:15:02,370
That means they don't want to offend me

228
00:15:02,370 --> 00:15:03,840
or the clan.

229
00:15:04,550 --> 00:15:06,950
They're still waiting to see what happens.

230
00:15:07,270 --> 00:15:09,750
The Ma family is a rising star in
the Three Central Offices.

231
00:15:09,750 --> 00:15:11,750
If he acts too attentively,

232
00:15:12,030 --> 00:15:13,720
the other advisors will surely worry

233
00:15:13,720 --> 00:15:16,780
that we're getting too close,
which would benefit him.

234
00:15:18,700 --> 00:15:20,430
This way, they won't dare to neglect me.

235
00:15:20,430 --> 00:15:23,290
I didn't expect Your Highness to
have such insight.

236
00:15:23,570 --> 00:15:25,430
It seems I was too narrow-minded.

237
00:15:26,560 --> 00:15:28,560
What insight could I possibly have?

238
00:15:29,880 --> 00:15:31,910
I was just thinking about

239
00:15:33,420 --> 00:15:35,420
what Xiu would do in this situation.

240
00:15:50,550 --> 00:15:53,090
I know the clan is going to repair
the Wayun Fortress,

241
00:15:53,090 --> 00:15:55,480
and Your Highness is in charge of
overseeing it.

242
00:15:55,480 --> 00:15:59,540
Therefore, I went through every part of
the Imperial Capital overnight,

243
00:15:59,910 --> 00:16:01,440
urgently mobilizing all liquid funds from

244
00:16:01,440 --> 00:16:03,280
the Ma family’s banks in all regions.

245
00:16:03,280 --> 00:16:05,360
Although it's not enough to
support the repairs,

246
00:16:05,360 --> 00:16:08,760
I hope it'll be a good start for
Your Highness's fundraising.

247
00:16:47,430 --> 00:16:50,150
I heard long ago that Your Highness's
favorite drink is osmanthus tea.

248
00:16:50,150 --> 00:16:53,810
Last year, I personally harvested
the osmanthus from the garden.

249
00:16:54,390 --> 00:16:55,790
I'm truly delighted that

250
00:16:56,360 --> 00:16:58,090
my wish can be fulfilled today.

251
00:16:59,000 --> 00:17:01,130
That's very thoughtful of you, Mr. Ma.

252
00:17:01,210 --> 00:17:02,660
I love osmanthus tea

253
00:17:03,000 --> 00:17:05,930
only because when I was little
and together with Xiu,

254
00:17:06,030 --> 00:17:07,160
he loved to drink it.

255
00:17:10,069 --> 00:17:11,240
I most admire

256
00:17:11,480 --> 00:17:14,210
someone like Your Highness,
who loves so deeply,

257
00:17:14,310 --> 00:17:15,829
because I am the same way.

258
00:17:20,329 --> 00:17:22,329
I'm sure Your Highness's visit here

259
00:17:22,510 --> 00:17:24,270
isn't solely because of me.

260
00:17:24,720 --> 00:17:27,170
Has the fundraising encountered
some obstacles?

261
00:17:27,170 --> 00:17:28,369
On my way back to the city,

262
00:17:28,369 --> 00:17:31,110
I also heard some disrespectful words
from Advisor He.

263
00:17:31,110 --> 00:17:33,590
Advisor He drove away my attendant
and spoke ill of me.

264
00:17:33,590 --> 00:17:35,520
This shows disrespect to the clan.

265
00:17:35,750 --> 00:17:36,830
I want to make an example of him

266
00:17:36,830 --> 00:17:39,240
to intimidate those advisors
who are unwilling to contribute.

267
00:17:39,240 --> 00:17:41,350
However, the powers behind
the Three Central Offices

268
00:17:41,350 --> 00:17:43,270
are deeply entangled and very complex.

269
00:17:43,270 --> 00:17:45,400
So I'd like to hear your advice, Mr. Ma.

270
00:17:48,480 --> 00:17:51,600
Advisor He's actions are
disrespectful to the clan,

271
00:17:52,510 --> 00:17:54,310
which is indeed disheartening.

272
00:17:55,270 --> 00:17:56,000
It's just...

273
00:17:57,640 --> 00:17:59,240
Please speak freely, Mr. Ma.

274
00:17:59,960 --> 00:18:01,290
If I continue speaking,

275
00:18:01,770 --> 00:18:03,640
I'm afraid I might end up like Advisor He,

276
00:18:03,640 --> 00:18:06,440
overstepping my bounds and
being disrespectful.

277
00:18:16,880 --> 00:18:18,680
Mr. Ma, what you're saying today

278
00:18:18,680 --> 00:18:20,680
is not in the capacity of an advisor,

279
00:18:22,110 --> 00:18:23,790
but rather as a friend giving advice

280
00:18:23,790 --> 00:18:24,850
to another friend.

281
00:18:24,960 --> 00:18:27,420
How could that be considered overstepping?

282
00:18:33,890 --> 00:18:36,110
The reason why Chieftain entrusted
this matter to Your Highness is that,

283
00:18:36,110 --> 00:18:38,640
on one hand, he couldn't
intervene directly;

284
00:18:38,880 --> 00:18:41,030
and on the other hand, it's a test
for Your Highness,

285
00:18:41,030 --> 00:18:43,160
to see if you have the political acumen

286
00:18:43,370 --> 00:18:45,690
befitting an heir to the clan, right?

287
00:18:48,290 --> 00:18:49,220
Then, what if...

288
00:18:49,840 --> 00:18:51,600
I mean, hypothetically,

289
00:18:52,590 --> 00:18:55,510
if Your Highness takes this chance
to severely punish Advisor He,

290
00:18:55,510 --> 00:18:58,900
the other nobles in the Three Central
Offices would surely petition together,

291
00:18:58,900 --> 00:19:02,690
accusing you of ruthless exaction
and deeming you unfit to govern.

292
00:19:03,200 --> 00:19:05,830
How should Your Highness
handle that situation then?

293
00:19:05,830 --> 00:19:07,830
After all, there's no law in Zichuan

294
00:19:07,870 --> 00:19:09,070
requiring merchants

295
00:19:09,070 --> 00:19:11,270
to donate for the clan's difficulties.

296
00:19:13,200 --> 00:19:14,990
If more than half of the members
of the Three Central Offices

297
00:19:14,990 --> 00:19:16,790
threaten to strike and boycott,

298
00:19:16,850 --> 00:19:17,980
Zichuan's finances

299
00:19:18,070 --> 00:19:20,240
would collapse within ten days.

300
00:19:20,730 --> 00:19:24,330
How do you think the Chieftain
would handle this, Your Highness?

301
00:19:24,650 --> 00:19:26,930
At worst, I'll follow the old precedent

302
00:19:27,830 --> 00:19:30,560
and nationalize the mining
and salt industries.

303
00:19:32,310 --> 00:19:34,570
This move does conform to the old system,

304
00:19:35,540 --> 00:19:39,310
but currently, the clan has no department
for commerce or salt affairs.

305
00:19:39,310 --> 00:19:41,270
If you were to actually implement it,

306
00:19:41,270 --> 00:19:43,440
without years of planning and preparation,

307
00:19:43,440 --> 00:19:46,350
it would be difficult to make a profit
in the short term.

308
00:19:46,350 --> 00:19:49,070
It might even lead to shortages of goods
in various regions,

309
00:19:49,070 --> 00:19:50,800
causing further civil unrest.

310
00:19:51,030 --> 00:19:52,510
So according to what you're saying,

311
00:19:52,510 --> 00:19:53,550
this money

312
00:19:53,550 --> 00:19:55,640
cannot be raised from the
Three Central Offices?

313
00:19:55,640 --> 00:19:56,970
That's not what I meant.

314
00:19:57,350 --> 00:19:59,180
Your Highness has issued
a fundraising notice,

315
00:19:59,180 --> 00:20:00,980
which is a way to test the waters.

316
00:20:01,850 --> 00:20:04,270
I believe most advisors have donated
something, more or less,

317
00:20:04,270 --> 00:20:06,930
but that was out of fear of
the clan's authority.

318
00:20:14,160 --> 00:20:16,690
If Your Highness is willing to
take a step back

319
00:20:16,960 --> 00:20:18,620
and use both carrot and stick,

320
00:20:19,110 --> 00:20:21,510
they will have no choice
but to compromise.

321
00:20:24,550 --> 00:20:26,480
Hold a charity banquet

322
00:20:26,480 --> 00:20:28,140
initiated in the clan's name.

323
00:20:28,480 --> 00:20:30,940
Those advisors can claim
they have no money,

324
00:20:31,600 --> 00:20:34,050
but their wealth and assets are there
for all to see.

325
00:20:34,050 --> 00:20:35,700
They can't possibly say they don't have

326
00:20:35,700 --> 00:20:37,280
even a single piece of precious antique
to offer, can they?

327
00:20:37,280 --> 00:20:40,170
Once they see the opportunity,
they'll be eager to participate.

328
00:20:40,170 --> 00:20:42,320
If there are clan treasures
that can be donated,

329
00:20:42,320 --> 00:20:44,780
they will be even more eager
to get involved.

330
00:20:45,040 --> 00:20:46,500
If there can be an auction,

331
00:20:46,990 --> 00:20:50,320
the price will likely soar,
bringing considerable income.

332
00:20:50,530 --> 00:20:52,550
I have quite a few jewels in my residence

333
00:20:52,550 --> 00:20:54,110
that can all be donated for sale.

334
00:20:54,110 --> 00:20:55,510
My father and uncle

335
00:20:55,530 --> 00:20:57,550
have also bestowed many precious items
upon me.

336
00:20:57,550 --> 00:20:59,590
I also have a collection of
valuable porcelain.

337
00:20:59,590 --> 00:21:01,200
I'll have my servants pack them up shortly

338
00:21:01,200 --> 00:21:03,110
and send them to
Your Highness's residence.

339
00:21:03,110 --> 00:21:05,450
Merchants have the strongest
sense of competition.

340
00:21:05,450 --> 00:21:07,550
When those advisors see how generous I am,

341
00:21:07,550 --> 00:21:10,550
they'll surely speculate that this move
will bring future benefits.

342
00:21:10,550 --> 00:21:12,510
They will definitely be lining up at
Your Highness's doorstep

343
00:21:12,510 --> 00:21:14,070
to deliver their treasures.

344
00:21:14,070 --> 00:21:16,680
At that time, I'll have a word with
the advisors I'm familiar with

345
00:21:16,680 --> 00:21:18,050
and explain a thing or two.

346
00:21:18,050 --> 00:21:20,400
This will surely stir things up.

347
00:21:26,270 --> 00:21:28,400
Yesterday's battle went pretty well.

348
00:21:28,400 --> 00:21:30,310
Although we didn't capture Bulu Village,

349
00:21:30,310 --> 00:21:32,680
we did get to test our strength.

350
00:21:33,400 --> 00:21:36,480
Turns out those people are
all equally weak.

351
00:21:38,550 --> 00:21:40,240
Today, you all eat and drink well.

352
00:21:40,240 --> 00:21:42,960
Tomorrow, let's take the sacred temple
in one go!

353
00:21:42,960 --> 00:21:44,240
Victory to the North Clan!

354
00:21:44,240 --> 00:21:45,700
Victory to the North Clan!

355
00:21:45,790 --> 00:21:47,520
Come on, have some vegetables.

356
00:21:49,110 --> 00:21:51,440
I said have some vegetables, not the meat.

357
00:21:56,400 --> 00:21:57,160
Now that

358
00:21:57,190 --> 00:21:59,210
we've already conquered most of Yuanzhou.

359
00:21:59,210 --> 00:22:01,100
If we take the sacred temple,

360
00:22:01,310 --> 00:22:03,030
then this rabble in Yuanzhou

361
00:22:03,200 --> 00:22:04,960
will lose their spiritual pillar.

362
00:22:04,960 --> 00:22:06,050
As for the remaining areas,

363
00:22:06,050 --> 00:22:07,710
we can attack however we want.

364
00:22:08,160 --> 00:22:09,400
As long as we capture the sacred temple,

365
00:22:09,400 --> 00:22:12,130
it's first come, first served
for what's inside.

366
00:22:18,350 --> 00:22:18,830
Eat.

367
00:22:19,830 --> 00:22:20,350
My Lord.

368
00:22:21,030 --> 00:22:22,920
The North Clan soldiers brought by Lu Di

369
00:22:22,920 --> 00:22:24,120
are less than 10,000.

370
00:22:24,270 --> 00:22:26,130
They're stationed near Longya Mountain.

371
00:22:26,130 --> 00:22:28,070
The combined forces of all races
in Yuanzhou

372
00:22:28,070 --> 00:22:29,350
are twice their number.

373
00:22:29,350 --> 00:22:31,080
Although we have a significant

374
00:22:31,680 --> 00:22:33,310
advantage in numbers,

375
00:22:33,790 --> 00:22:36,680
last time, Lu Di, with just
a few thousand soilders,

376
00:22:36,700 --> 00:22:38,390
defeated us thoroughly.

377
00:22:38,720 --> 00:22:39,920
If they attack again,

378
00:22:39,960 --> 00:22:41,290
I estimate their target

379
00:22:41,350 --> 00:22:43,950
will be the sacred temple
behind Bulu Village.

380
00:22:44,510 --> 00:22:46,030
Although this time, Elder Budan

381
00:22:46,030 --> 00:22:48,440
has publicly ordered all races to unite,

382
00:22:48,880 --> 00:22:52,210
these people have been fighting separately
for a long time.

383
00:22:52,240 --> 00:22:53,680
I'm afraid they may have agreed
on the surface,

384
00:22:53,680 --> 00:22:55,810
but in reality, it won't be effective.

385
00:22:55,880 --> 00:22:56,440
Luo Jie.

386
00:22:57,480 --> 00:22:59,200
I asked you to gather the
leaders of each race

387
00:22:59,200 --> 00:23:01,510
for pre-battle assignments.
How's that going?

388
00:23:01,510 --> 00:23:03,440
I'm almost too embarrassed to say,

389
00:23:03,510 --> 00:23:05,720
but the Snake Race and the Gnomes

390
00:23:05,920 --> 00:23:07,720
played rock-paper-scissors to decide
who guards the city gate.

391
00:23:07,720 --> 00:23:08,850
The Snake Race lost,

392
00:23:09,110 --> 00:23:11,350
but they refused to honor the bet
and went back on their word.

393
00:23:11,350 --> 00:23:12,350
And then there's the Dragon Race.

394
00:23:12,350 --> 00:23:15,210
The Dragon Race was cooperating
well with the Orcs,

395
00:23:15,270 --> 00:23:16,880
but when the Dragon Race found out
that the Orcs' supplies

396
00:23:16,880 --> 00:23:18,340
far exceeded their own...

397
00:23:18,440 --> 00:23:19,350
You know,

398
00:23:19,480 --> 00:23:21,100
those Orcs are all like that,

399
00:23:21,340 --> 00:23:22,740
with such big appetites.

400
00:23:22,960 --> 00:23:25,830
But the Dragon Race doesn't care.
They just want food.

401
00:23:25,830 --> 00:23:27,440
In this case,

402
00:23:27,470 --> 00:23:29,270
the Elves are the most sensible.

403
00:23:30,880 --> 00:23:31,680
Look at this.

404
00:23:33,070 --> 00:23:34,400
This is the report they
submitted privately.

405
00:23:34,400 --> 00:23:36,830
Submitting private reports doesn't
seem like the Elves' style.

406
00:23:36,830 --> 00:23:39,230
This isn't a complaint, but a resignation.

407
00:23:39,880 --> 00:23:40,790
They wrote so long,

408
00:23:40,790 --> 00:23:42,250
but the message is simple:

409
00:23:42,310 --> 00:23:43,960
they're saying they lack
the ability to help,

410
00:23:43,960 --> 00:23:45,880
so we should leave them out of it.

411
00:23:47,350 --> 00:23:50,270
My Lord! We crouched in ambush all night

412
00:23:50,400 --> 00:23:52,400
and finally caught a North Clan soldier.

413
00:23:52,400 --> 00:23:54,000
They have a cavalry unit
that's reached here,

414
00:23:54,000 --> 00:23:55,640
and their supply wagons have arrived here.

415
00:23:55,640 --> 00:23:56,880
This is great news.

416
00:23:57,110 --> 00:23:58,240
They've retreated?

417
00:23:58,240 --> 00:24:00,960
No, they're coming to attack.

418
00:24:01,070 --> 00:24:01,750
Chief.

419
00:24:02,270 --> 00:24:03,720
Look at the mess we're in now.

420
00:24:03,720 --> 00:24:04,920
Everyone's fighting their own battles.

421
00:24:04,920 --> 00:24:07,200
Even if they come to attack,
we can't handle it.

422
00:24:07,200 --> 00:24:08,930
What's there to be happy about?

423
00:24:11,070 --> 00:24:13,480
These people are giving me a headache
with all this arguing.

424
00:24:13,480 --> 00:24:16,000
I just want one battle, to die and
be done with it.

425
00:24:16,000 --> 00:24:18,400
Let Lu Di give us a quick end.

426
00:24:41,240 --> 00:24:43,770
Why should we, the Snake Race,
be used as bait?

427
00:24:43,790 --> 00:24:45,750
Are you looking down on our strength?

428
00:24:45,750 --> 00:24:48,550
We can fight! We want to stand
in front of the sacred temple.

429
00:24:48,550 --> 00:24:50,920
We'll give those North Clan brats
a taste of our fists!

430
00:24:50,920 --> 00:24:51,680
We won't be

431
00:24:51,680 --> 00:24:53,000
hiding in the woods, throwing stones,

432
00:24:53,000 --> 00:24:54,130
or setting up ropes.

433
00:24:54,790 --> 00:24:56,960
For those petty tricks,

434
00:24:56,960 --> 00:24:59,200
we'd better leave them to
the little Elves.

435
00:24:59,200 --> 00:25:00,160
Who are you calling little?

436
00:25:00,160 --> 00:25:01,000
I think

437
00:25:01,200 --> 00:25:03,270
the Dragon Race should be the bait.

438
00:25:03,590 --> 00:25:04,640
You don't even have to fight.

439
00:25:04,640 --> 00:25:06,480
All you have to do is run for your lives.

440
00:25:06,480 --> 00:25:08,110
What did you just say?

441
00:25:08,110 --> 00:25:09,030
Say that again!

442
00:25:09,030 --> 00:25:10,030
You want to fight, huh?

443
00:25:10,030 --> 00:25:10,830
What did I say?

444
00:25:11,160 --> 00:25:12,400
Bring it on!

445
00:25:12,720 --> 00:25:14,120
Stop arguing, all of you!

446
00:25:17,270 --> 00:25:18,680
I trust Lord Xiu.

447
00:25:20,350 --> 00:25:22,350
Let's hear what he has to say, okay?

448
00:25:26,030 --> 00:25:26,830
Go ahead.

449
00:25:28,640 --> 00:25:29,680
If you ask me,

450
00:25:32,750 --> 00:25:34,350
you should all stop fighting

451
00:25:35,750 --> 00:25:37,200
and just save yourselves.

452
00:25:37,200 --> 00:25:37,960
How can we do that?

453
00:25:37,960 --> 00:25:38,640
Why not?

454
00:25:38,830 --> 00:25:40,690
The North Clan is about to attack,

455
00:25:41,030 --> 00:25:42,490
and what are you all doing?

456
00:25:43,270 --> 00:25:45,070
Still arguing endlessly here.

457
00:25:46,200 --> 00:25:49,350
I think you might as well invite Lu Di in

458
00:25:49,640 --> 00:25:51,240
and give him your sacred temple

459
00:25:51,240 --> 00:25:53,350
as a welcoming gift.

460
00:25:53,640 --> 00:25:54,960
We'll live or die with the sacred temple!

461
00:25:54,960 --> 00:25:56,790
How can we surrender just like that?
We won't surrender!

462
00:25:56,790 --> 00:25:58,830
Right, we won't surrender!

463
00:25:58,830 --> 00:26:01,640
Fine, you said it.

464
00:26:03,070 --> 00:26:04,790
Let me be blunt then.

465
00:26:05,640 --> 00:26:07,370
My men of the Xiu Battalion and I

466
00:26:07,550 --> 00:26:09,110
have already packed our bags

467
00:26:09,110 --> 00:26:11,110
and are ready to retreat at any time.

468
00:26:11,750 --> 00:26:13,750
Whether the sacred temple
can be preserved

469
00:26:13,750 --> 00:26:16,170
and whether Yuanzhou can find peace,

470
00:26:16,750 --> 00:26:17,960
it's all up to you.

471
00:26:19,110 --> 00:26:19,920
What is he doing?

472
00:26:19,920 --> 00:26:21,680
What Lord Xiu means is that

473
00:26:21,680 --> 00:26:23,120
If you want to live,

474
00:26:23,770 --> 00:26:25,070
shut your mouths.

475
00:26:27,510 --> 00:26:28,160
Guys.

476
00:26:29,440 --> 00:26:30,500
Let me ask you this:

477
00:26:30,720 --> 00:26:32,920
in terms of speed and climbing ability,

478
00:26:34,270 --> 00:26:37,160
who's better than the Snake Race?

479
00:26:40,070 --> 00:26:42,790
So, other than the Snake Race,

480
00:26:43,160 --> 00:26:45,200
who's more suitable to be the bait?

481
00:26:46,350 --> 00:26:47,440
And you Elves.

482
00:26:48,200 --> 00:26:50,530
You're good at archery and setting traps.

483
00:26:50,790 --> 00:26:52,830
I need you to lead everyone

484
00:26:52,830 --> 00:26:54,290
to set up traps in advance.

485
00:26:55,030 --> 00:26:56,090
And you Dragon Race

486
00:26:56,610 --> 00:26:58,030
is born with incredible arm strength

487
00:26:58,030 --> 00:26:59,310
and fighting prowess.

488
00:27:00,200 --> 00:27:02,590
You're perfect for dealing with the
North Clan members who fall into the traps

489
00:27:02,590 --> 00:27:04,320
and confronting them head-on.

490
00:27:04,880 --> 00:27:05,810
This time, I hope

491
00:27:06,310 --> 00:27:08,570
everyone can bring out their best skills

492
00:27:08,750 --> 00:27:10,550
and show them what we're made of.

493
00:27:20,240 --> 00:27:22,720
Let me first explain my plan.

494
00:27:23,400 --> 00:27:27,270
First, I need the Snake Race
to split into two groups

495
00:27:28,160 --> 00:27:29,790
and guard outside Bulu Village.

496
00:27:29,790 --> 00:27:32,250
If you encounter the enemy,
just curse them.

497
00:27:32,510 --> 00:27:34,270
Shout all those foul words

498
00:27:34,400 --> 00:27:35,440
right at them.

499
00:27:35,550 --> 00:27:38,160
But remember, don't engage in combat.

500
00:27:40,000 --> 00:27:42,920
When the time comes,

501
00:27:43,110 --> 00:27:44,640
lead them all into the city.

502
00:27:44,720 --> 00:27:45,790
Later,

503
00:27:45,790 --> 00:27:48,240
the Dragon Race and the Elves
will take over.

504
00:27:48,240 --> 00:27:51,480
What if they don't come to support us?

505
00:27:53,680 --> 00:27:56,790
This is the biggest problem with
all the races of Yuanzhou:

506
00:27:56,790 --> 00:27:58,590
a lack of trust among each other.

507
00:27:59,720 --> 00:28:01,350
If the Dragon Race and Elves

508
00:28:01,590 --> 00:28:03,720
don't provide support as instructed,

509
00:28:05,960 --> 00:28:09,440
then my Xiu Battalion will stand by
and do nothing.

510
00:28:09,790 --> 00:28:12,590
At that time, you'll have to
watch helplessly

511
00:28:12,590 --> 00:28:14,400
as your Elder Budan

512
00:28:15,240 --> 00:28:16,970
has his head chopped off by Lu Di

513
00:28:17,000 --> 00:28:20,200
and your sacred temple gets desecrated
by the North Clan.

514
00:28:23,160 --> 00:28:23,980
And this place

515
00:28:24,590 --> 00:28:26,560
will be your final resting place.

516
00:28:29,000 --> 00:28:29,720
Guys.

517
00:28:32,640 --> 00:28:36,310
Only by unity and coordination

518
00:28:36,590 --> 00:28:38,920
do we have a chance of
winning this battle,

519
00:28:39,070 --> 00:28:42,480
and only then will Yuanzhou have
any hope of survival.

520
00:28:43,240 --> 00:28:45,310
Unite as one, defend the sacred temple!

521
00:28:45,310 --> 00:28:47,320
Unite as one, defend the sacred temple!

522
00:28:47,320 --> 00:28:49,140
Unite as one, defend the sacred temple!

523
00:28:49,140 --> 00:28:51,260
Unite as one, defend the sacred temple!

524
